%N A395886 Number of oriented polyominoes in the {7,6} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%C A395886 For oriented polyominoes, chiral pairs are counted as two.
%H A395886 <a href="https://oeis.org/wiki/PF-Non-Euclidean">Index entries for sequences related to non-euclidean polyforms</a>
%F A395886 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of oriented {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q. In this case, P{p,oo} = A389561.
%t A395886 (* Cf. A394862 with p=7 and q=6. *)
%Y A395886 Cf. A389561, A393736, A394862.
